LatexCommand cite
key "BrennerVLA2007,ShuPeckOwnership2011"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
 If we are rich we see gain as little - thereby reducing our.
 If someone is more educated, they might become more conservative.
 negative changes loom larger than positive changes.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To consider a particular solution of the Equations 
