status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
In the general approach for evolution of the savings rate, the consumer
 would have a certain expected savings process - whose expectation (or discounti
ng) would determine the participation in quality while the evolution of
 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{t}$
\end_inset

 itself would determine We assume that the utility of the consumer evolves
 with a general stochastic process the
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{alignat}{1}
ds & =\mu(A_{t},\eta_{t})dt+\sigma(\kappa_{t})dW\label{eq:savings_stochastic_evolution}
\end{alignat}

\end_inset


\end_layout

